---
title: Roast Chicken & Crispy Prosciutto with Creamy Dijon Sauce, Mash & Veggies
description: Roast chicken and mash is a homey classic, but let’s take it up a notch! Indulge in this glowing golden chicken, roasted to perfection, paired with a luxuriously smooth mash, mustard sauce and crispy prosciutto. This dish is fit for the stars!
